data.value:
To create a user, select the create button and fill out the required information. To edit an existing user's information, select their information from the table, press 'edit' and enter their new details. To delete an user, select their informaiton from the table and select 'delete.
NOTE AccessLevel 2 = Administrator" AccessLevel 1 = Coach AccessLevel 0 = Student
